                            <ul class="list-disc list-inside space-y-2">
                                <li>Study types of 3D printing (focus on FDM).</li>
                                <li>Understand printer parts: Frame, Bed, Extruder, etc.</li>
                                <li>Watch a demo of a 3D printer in action.</li>
                            </ul>
