                        <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold text-sky-700">Day 2: Materials & Safety</h2>
                    </div>
                    <div class="mt-4 grid md:grid-cols-2 gap-6 items-center">
                        <div class="text-gray-700 space-y-3">
                            <p>Learn about the different plastics used for printing and crucial safety measures to protect yourself and your printer.</p>
                             <ul class="list-disc list-inside space-y-2">
                                <li>Filaments: PLA, ABS, PETG, TPU.</li>
                                <li>Bed adhesion methods (tape, glue, heated bed).</li>
                                <li>Safety: Hot nozzle, moving parts, ventilation.</li>
                            </ul>
                        </div>
                        <img src="https://placehold.co/600x400/0ea5e9/ffffff?text=Filament+Spools" alt="Filament Spools" class="rounded-lg object-cover w-full h-full">
