                        <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold text-indigo-700">Day 3: Intro to CAD & STL Files</h2>
                    </div>
                    <div class="mt-4 grid md:grid-cols-2 gap-6 items-center">
                        <div class="text-gray-700 space-y-3">
                             <p>Dive into the world of 3D design. Learn how to create your own models or find existing ones to print.</p>
                             <ul class="list-disc list-inside space-y-2">
                                <li>3D Design Software (TinkerCAD, Fusion360).</li>
                                <li>Understand the STL file format.</li>
                                <li>Download free models from Thingiverse/Printables.</li>
                            </ul>
                        </div>
                        <img src="https://placehold.co/600x400/6366f1/ffffff?text=CAD+Interface" alt="CAD Software Interface" class="rounded-lg object-cover w-full h-full">
