            <!-- Day 4 -->
            <div id="day-4" class="day-card bg-white rounded-xl shadow-lg overflow-hidden">
                <div class="p-6 md:p-8">
                    <div class="flex justify-between items-start">
                        <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold text-purple-700">Day 4: Slicing Software</h2>
                    </div>
                    <div class="mt-4 grid md:grid-cols-2 gap-6 items-center">
                        <div class="text-gray-700 space-y-3">
                            <p>Learn how a <span class="font-semibold text-purple-800">slicer</span> converts your 3D model (STL) into instructions (G-code) that the printer can understand.</p>
                            <ul class="list-disc list-inside space-y-2">
                                <li>Install Cura or PrusaSlicer.</li>
                                <li>Key settings: Layer height, infill, supports.</li>
                                <li>Preview toolpaths before printing.</li>
                            </ul>
                        </div>
                        <img src="https://placehold.co/600x400/9333ea/ffffff?text=Slicer+Software" alt="Slicer Software" class="rounded-lg object-cover w-full h-full">
                    </div>
                </div>
            </div>

            <!-- Day 5 -->
            <div id="day-5" class="day-card bg-white rounded-xl shadow-lg overflow-hidden">
                <div class="p-6 md:p-8">
                    <div class="flex justify-between items-start">
                        <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold text-pink-700">Day 5: First Print & Calibration</h2>
                    </div>
                    <div class="mt-4 grid md:grid-cols-2 gap-6 items-center">
                        <div class="text-gray-700 space-y-3">
                            <p>Time to get hands-on! Proper calibration, especially <span class="font-semibold text-pink-800">bed leveling</span>, is the key to a successful first print.</p>
                             <ul class="list-disc list-inside space-y-2">
                                <li>Learn why bed leveling matters.</li>
                                <li>Print a test model like a calibration cube or Benchy.</li>
                                <li>Observe for common issues (warping, stringing).</li>
                            </ul>
                        </div>
                        <img src="https://placehold.co/600x400/ec4899/ffffff?text=First+Print" alt="First 3D Print" class="rounded-lg object-cover w-full h-full">
