                        <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold text-orange-700">Day 7: Post-Processing & Beyond</h2>
                    </div>
                    <div class="mt-4 grid md:grid-cols-2 gap-6 items-center">
                        <div class="text-gray-700 space-y-3">
                             <p>The print finishing is just the beginning. Learn how to clean up your prints and explore more advanced topics.</p>
                            <ul class="list-disc list-inside space-y-2">
                                <li>Post-processing: sanding, painting, smoothing.</li>
                                <li>Explore advanced filaments (wood, carbon-fiber).</li>
                                <li>Print a useful object like a phone stand.</li>
